"text": "Implemented a focused coverage test for the active dynamic-access class.\n\nAdded:\n\n- `tests/src/org.glassfish.jersey.core/jersey-server/2.34/src/test/java/org_glassfish_jersey_core/jersey_server/VfsSchemeResourceFinderFactoryInnerVfsResourceFinderTest.java`\n\nWhat it covers:\n\n- Exercises Jersey’s public `PackageNamesScanner` path for `vfs:` URLs.\n- Installs a bounded in-memory `vfs` URL handler.\n- Provides a `VirtualFile` object with the public VFS-style methods expected by Jersey.\n- Drives scanning, `next()`, and `open()` so execution reaches:\n  - `Class#getMethod(...)` in `bindMethod0`\n  - `Method#invoke(...)` in `invoke`\n\nI did not run compilation or tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c34d9f2d2866ef70169fea5681bc88197900d23125eb156f8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 705, "output": 1117, "cacheRead": 21504, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 23326, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778296154349, "responseId": "resp_0c34d9f2d2866ef70169fea55ae0cc8197bb36b0ed2e0d4be1"}, "toolResults": []}
